title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 19 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 19 2021
description:
Ohio Congressman Jim Jordan has a broad discussion with Clay and Buck: the Rittenhouse verdict that they applaud, Biden DOJ outrageously targeting parents, and why the Democrat spending bill will cause current inflation to skyrocket. Are we going to see violence on the streets of Kenosha? Live coverage of Rittenhouse defense attorney, Mark Richards, taking a victory lap. C&B take lively calls on this important Open Line Friday.
